<p>For this first Premium episode of June, John and Dave talk through all KINDS of topics, answering your questions about Mac disk tools, iPad documents, runaway Rosettas, Mac Spyware, and more. Subscribe today (it&rsquo;s only $25 for 6 months!), support your two favorite geeks, and enjoy!</p>
